'''''Vrexlir''''' was a [[Xiytiar-class heavy transport|''Xiytiar''-class heavy transport]] delivering sensors to [[Bretie Facility]] as part of the [[TIE Experimental Project]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], shortly before [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Demetrius Zaarin]]'s attempted coup. It was accompanied by its sister ship, the ''[[Dandi]]''.

